{"id":607712,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2019/03/【立此存照】新疆大学、伊犁师范大学撤去维语校/","date":"2019-03-20T07:15:51Z","modified":"2019-03-20T07:15:51Z","title":"【立此存照】新疆大学、伊犁师范大学撤去维语校徽","content":"<p>3月19日，有网友爆料，新疆大学与伊犁师范大学（学院）近期均撤换了校徽，将原校徽中的维语删除，目前尚不清楚是否还有新疆其他高校也更换了校徽。</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-607716\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/03/D2DWuqfX4AAt_4I.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"720\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/03/D2DWuqfX4AAt_4I.jpg 833w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/03/D2DWuqfX4AAt_4I-208x300.jpg 208w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/03/D2DWuqfX4AAt_4I-768x1106.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/03/D2DWuqfX4AAt_4I-711x1024.jpg 711w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-607717\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/03/Image-from-iOS-7.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"636\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/03/Image-from-iOS-7.jpg 629w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/03/Image-from-iOS-7-236x300.jpg 236w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p>这一举措很显然是为了去除维族主体民族意识的举措，因为除了删除“维语元素”，校徽其他方面并未做任何设计上的修改，而“新疆大学”的新版校徽，还将“天山”的元素同时去除。</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_607718\" style=\"width: 560px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-607718\" class=\"wp-image-607718\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/03/Image-from-iOS-1-2.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"551\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/03/Image-from-iOS-1-2.jpg 720w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/03/Image-from-iOS-1-2-150x150.jpg 150w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/03/Image-from-iOS-1-2-300x300.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/03/Image-from-iOS-1-2-70x70.jpg 70w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/03/Image-from-iOS-1-2-50x50.jpg 50w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-607718\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">上面两图为旧版 下面两图为新版</p></div>\n<p>在部分网友口径中称这是“培养民族共同体意识”、“删除了不合时宜的元素”。</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-607715\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/03/D2DWuqnW0AEn2bL.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"726\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/03/D2DWuqnW0AEn2bL.jpg 826w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/03/D2DWuqnW0AEn2bL-207x300.jpg 207w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/03/D2DWuqnW0AEn2bL-768x1116.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/03/D2DWuqnW0AEn2bL-705x1024.jpg 705w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-607714\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/03/新疆.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"637\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/03/新疆.png 743w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/03/新疆-235x300.png 235w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n","author":1003,"categories":[18271,18270,18269,27949],"tags":[9941,30512,31919,12056,17915,12055,9503,26070]}